snippet.title: Let's Play: The Falconeer - Warrior Edition [Preview]
snippet.description: Take up the challenge of flying your mighty falcon to defend the skies, patrol, and shoot down any threats to your empire. While perhaps not an intended problem, landing may be the most difficult thing in the game of all... at least for me. This still has a while to bake though, it won't formally release until August.
